10. exd4 Nh5
{ Attacking the active bishop and planning to play ...e5 in some moment. } 11.
Bh2
{ A representative game in that position is between Demakov,V - Datler, W , 2017, 1/2. }
11... Bh6
{ The dark-squared bishop for Black is more active on the h6-c1 diagonal. } 12.
O-O Nf4
{ With the idea of ...Bf5, ...a5, ...a4 & ...Rd8 to consolidate and obtain space advantage. }
