9. exd4 Qxa1 10. dxc5 Qxa2
{ There is not full compensation for White. Both players castle, but White may capture on f6 to ruin the black king's pawn cover. However, they don't have enough pieces to initiate a kingside attack. With the pawn already on f6, Black may continue with ...e6-e5 and develop their light-squared bishop. }
