4... cxd4 { The most competitive move. } 5. Nb5
{ Fails to ...e7-e5 and makes no sense for this concrete position. } 5... e5
{ Black has an extra pawn and there are some interesting complications in Black's favor after  6.Bg3  a6!  . }
