{ 14.a4  weakens the knight's position on b3 and Black may continue with  14...Bf5  15.Qd1  White's queen is tied down to the knight on b3. }
14... a4 15. Nbd2 e5
{ Black succeeds in playing ...e5, one of their major plans in London System. }
16. Nxe5 Bxe5 17. Bxh5 gxh5 18. dxe5 Nxe5
{ And Black gets a clear plan to attack on the kingside with ...Qg6 and ...f3. }
