{ Looks like a tempo move, but this is a clear mistake. } 17... Nxf4 18. Nxb6
Nxe2+ 19. Kh1 axb6
{ Black has compensation of 3 minor pieces for the queen, but the position is unclear. The black plan depends on what White intends. }
