9. Rb1 Qa3
{ 9...Qc3 can be played as well, but   9...Qa2  is a critical mistake.  10.Ra1  attacking the queen,  10...Qb2  and  11.Nb5  ,  the a6-pawn is pinned, because of the open a-file. }
