[Result "*"]

1. d4 d5 2. Bf4 c5 3. e3 Nf6 4. Nf3 Nc6 5. Nbd2
{ One of the most tricky options. White saves a tempo and doesn't play c3 but sacrifices the b2-pawn and tries to take the advantage of their lead in development. }
